Title: The Soldiers of Pancho Villa
Writer: José Bolaños, Ricardo Garibay (dialogue), Ricardo Garibay (screenplay), Ismael Rodríguez, José Luis de Celis (dialogue), José Luis de Celis (screenplay)
Actors: María Félix, Dolores del Rio, Emilio Fernández, Antonio Aguilar
Plot: The Cucaracha is a brave woman soldier who leads a group of similar women into the fray against the forces of the Villa colonel, Zeta.
